<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="i-beg-to-differ">I beg to differ</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>恕我不敢苟同：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>—Only those who have a lot in common can get along well.
只有那些志趣相投的人才能相处融洽。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I beg to differ. Opposites sometimes do attract.
抱歉，我不敢苟同。意见相反的人有时也会互相吸引。</p><footer>2016 江苏</footer></div></div>